{"h260b4d86g3502g44bega8b1gd7c6af9c85df": ["You're here - good. Come with me.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "33bd99f9-fad6-96c4-e9eb-a308c545cc9d"], "hf2c971d1g1eedg4c72ga89eg087f38727146": ["Now, lie down.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "3500a3e5-d7b4-1c43-415f-118a72b0affb"], "h9593d90agef9ag42edgb10agd6fed8a1df17": ["<i>Do as she says.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "2a8044d0-9b76-bd34-7b2b-82b091116f03"], "h8140f0ccga6e1g43bfg9880g347dcba2b6cb": ["Care to tell me why?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "5ecc6a64-a28f-3d49-70b0-55551626b281"], "hf76baa97g0964g4d30g9948gc71d0f9cec6d": ["*An image of her naked body against yours flashes into your mind.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "9fecb335-bee2-b9cd-4a19-eb2ca410ae0d"], "h2afb9045gdd01g4e18ga1b0g2a7930062322": ["Do not speak. Just do as I say.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "c028e2c1-e2b7-23fc-90d5-adace8d1b69e"], "h996f682agda96g4fdega0e3g1911b982d5ae": ["I think we need to know each other a little better first.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "b177bbdc-a567-b859-b77e-9b1050ba0e76"], "h538fa24eg395eg494ag831ag378b7fb09cc3": ["I have seen your mind - I know everything I need to know.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "a8188a9b-e713-9c4d-523e-b9d44af80462"], "h967fcbb0g5fd1g4147gb9e3g27b95e6885e0": ["Now, silence. Lie down.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "a3ef9a24-40c1-17b9-0bcf-f0a932e3c11f"], "hf77b675eg420ag4887gb8fbged2b668a0774": ["<i>Do as she says.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "cde700b9-ef85-dc7e-eb97-7bafef53f0b9"], "hda52f25fge7c3g449cga49fg87e7d7ac9b9a": ["You learn fast.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "762e06d3-c4a9-8169-f1ff-c6621a2e72e4"], "h6ffb6f3cga40dg40b7gbe45g707e83cd379e": ["Your obedience will make this more enjoyable for both of us. Tell me what you want.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "ccf65ea5-b9c4-199c-f220-9041fd65792a"], "h164dc4cagbf77g4a48g826dgf585201f6eb3": ["I want you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "d6c645cf-b077-20a9-8722-f8f4c510a32d"], "h06bb1a8ag9c39g4ccag8b23g0f12554c688b": ["And you shall have me.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "237740ea-2316-d51c-52cf-e26e5dd1f49c"], "h19e42890gff07g4bfdgbff1g73cadef09eaa": ["*As your bodies lock together, so do your minds. Her whole being is laid bare before you.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "dcb0798f-bf98-9bea-03ab-3f9b9c2a8599"], "h91d44a05g28dcg4e2bg9006gb7ed87e9dcab": ["*And half-hidden at the centre of her desire, you discover something unexpected - fear.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "7bdbe85e-8fc9-a491-a539-57f4c6eee070"], "h36daf935g0f8fg4094gb790g0b19546296b1": ["<i>Focus on her desire.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "7a494769-5ab7-7f4d-a85a-feae01394318"], "h17a5a8ceg054bg4229gba85g678e86d23711": ["I would have you by my side in Menzoberranzan when our work on the surface is done.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "0fc2f3c7-687e-e4af-6fea-93c4bca7ef57"], "h26363219g5f86g4a3fg87f6gf3dd6441ec1e": ["But for now, it will be good to fight alongside you. Rest. Tomorrow, we will have fresh orders.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "f5a1ebd6-5eb0-32a0-95d4-d7ba627859c2"], "h59695b9fg8ccfg4260g921dg79c40e07418e": ["<i>Push deeper into her fears.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "cec2f9ab-7ce2-8584-6c3d-d07a2da26b77"], "hecac19c5gc0bag41b2g9bd0g4f0e73c4bf3f": ["*She flinches as layers of her psyche peel back, revealing the scars of a life spent anticipating a knife in the back.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "51aecf09-cd02-25eb-f7c6-14380ac6c20f"], "hd2dac7fdg941cg4e6egbabcgb85df6d9349b": ["*The memories of countless dead, slain too soon - not just enemies, but family, friends, lovers.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "607ded2c-d0ff-33f6-7078-2432ab5a8640"], "h796beb74g3291g4bb3ga989g8f968e048886": ["That was not yours to see.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "9c8f12be-dd16-33f6-e4c3-76a735378c9d"], "h7c58ef79gf8d0g46b6g97cag5de6c944ce54": ["I'm sorry - I meant no harm.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "20cb224b-8a92-3791-656d-3bf43ba236c3"], "he540ba2fg419cg484fg823ag6693839f3655": ["You are incapable of harming me. Get out of my sight.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "c8d21404-bbe4-dd5e-d646-0aaf4ec47f1f"], "hfe677950g807fg48bega3d4gd0ee8513fb1b": ["There's no shame in being afraid.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "3635d5f8-904c-ff04-eaf0-12d85b4733fb"], "ha419c115gf1b7g4ff8g8c80gd5cd140e6362": ["I harnessed my fear long ago - it sharpens me. You would do well to do the same.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "5f5a7e40-f00a-0056-0ca0-b2961edb0ca1"], "h54720a07g00cbg4004g8374g501d9ec9fa20": ["You're nothing but a coward.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "bfce9a58-05c6-05c3-8229-776f249be5e0"], "hff96d69fgcd52g4bf5gb220g8e64e10367c5": ["Leave. <i>Now</i>.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "963e42c7-1b02-b695-f7d0-c44a20b7a49b"], "he02b25e1ge78dg448ag8e78g3e81b5c5e2bd": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "ba9015d9-8db7-c5de-b01c-478a614df86f"], "h922cffd2gf5d4g4b19g8c7cg4c39e6587dcc": ["<i>Push deeper into her fears.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "18da2223-e583-97db-96ed-eb7ffb3028db"], "h255aa14fge5a5g43acg9a85gcfc10153c51d": ["My body could have been yours, but some things are mine alone. <i>Leave.</i>", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "ee315e05-2ab5-8d35-a6fc-00c410c30f56"], "ha328e12dgbbedg435cg8f56g3216f1474760": ["Not this. I want to leave.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "7674ffa8-512c-4f96-4a2c-89e3e5470828"], "h368aad7fg6d7dg43efgb17cg708007ccdaae": ["Then go - rest. We will discuss our next move in the morning.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "4a2dad79-e20f-855e-41d0-89f136c6c9e6"], "h275ba322g9881g4903gba5eg3361ac3ebaab": ["This isn't my idea of a good time.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "cad74888-c236-c786-1a0f-d570f375576d"], "hdb0a42bbg5bbfg46d7g9eaagb57661c71fe4": ["Then leave. You would only have disappointed me.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "8237d0b1-d279-06b8-230a-c4d34fd93234"], "h0608d0adgcbbeg4252g91afg6f631eb2a296": ["<i>You</i> lie down.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "f9714869-1a71-0b38-6baa-e6fbfffb9923"], "hceb45cc9ge351g4416gb389g5b7f81ac699a": ["Then I am yours.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "ba27900c-b5f5-cd9e-f979-c20d87fab00f"], "ha0994a34g5265g4cfeg95b1gcf949072e1bc": ["You couldn't control me with an army at your back. Do as I say, or get out of my sight.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "c0a694cd-4c23-8cb8-93dd-70f0dcf83522"], "ha9bed6b0g7805g4c3cg8080g2f858d22e4c3": ["Is this a seduction or a sacrifice?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "3060b9e5-eec5-cf9f-063a-b28ce0848b35"], "h9b5e41c4g6d6cg4767gbfd7g372313359e54": ["Neither. It is an instruction.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithDrow.html", "7adc1c03-9e07-92d9-1ae1-ad1ca55e702b"]}